cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the AMF IP address to an unreachable network (10.0.0.1) prevents the CU from establishing NG interface connection with the AMF, leading to registration failures.

du.explanation_en: Shifting the absolute SSB frequency by 1 unit causes misalignment with the expected SSB position, resulting in UE inability to detect and synchronize with the cell.
